name: mega_cross_unless_array_set_logic
section: codegen-cross-layer-stress
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: unless + array-as-function + mutating set + contains? must compose.
law: (= (with [xs [{a} {b}] s (set)] (do (unless {p} (conj! s (xs 0))) (contains? s {a}))) (not {p}))
